Class Entities

java.lang.Object
CsvToJsonConverter.Entities
class Entities extends Object
Container class grouping all extracted entities by their type AND including the collection information for the final JSON output structure.

  • Constructor Details

    • Entities

      public Entities(Set<Artifact> artifactsSet, Set<Item> itemsSet, Set<Document> documentsSet, Set<Person> peopleSet, Set<Organization> organizationsSet, Set<Category> categoriesSet, Set<Material> materialsSet)
      Constructs an Entities object. It converts the provided Sets of unique entities (gathered during parsing) into Lists suitable for JSON serialization. The CollectionInfo is initialized internally as a List.
      Parameters:
      artifactsSet - Set of unique Artifact entities.
      itemsSet - Set of unique Item entities.
      documentsSet - Set of unique Document entities.
      peopleSet - Set of unique Person entities.
      organizationsSet - Set of unique Organization entities.
      categoriesSet - Set of unique Category entities.
      materialsSet - Set of unique Material entities.
